      "skos:example": "A vendor makes an offer to receive a particular amount of money in exchange for the offered product; an offer to receive a home in exchange for an amount of money.",
      "skos:prefLabel": "offers to receive",
      "skos:scopeNote": "This will most often be an amount of money, but could be anything of value, as in swaps."
    },
